{"word":"ἐπιθαλάμιος","slug":"ἐπιθαλάμιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιθαλάμιος</b></el> <el>(ἐπι-θᾰλάμιος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θάλαμος'><el>θάλαμος</el></a>\n<p/><i>nuptial</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>: as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>, <el>ἐπιθαλάμιος, ὁ</el> or <el>ἡ</el> (<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>ὕμνος</el> or <el>ᾠδή</el>), <i>the bridal song</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/>"}]}